Description: Island Mountain MAI on-prem inference and compliance platform
 The MAI server provides REST and gRPC inference endpoints with an
 integrated compliance layer (Lamprey) that enforces HIPAA, ITAR, and
 tribal data-sovereignty (OCAP) policy at request time. This package
 ships the production "ship" profile only; demo defaults are rejected
 by the production guard on every boot.
 .
 Components installed:
   * mai-api      - REST + gRPC inference server (systemd unit included)
   * mai-ship-validate - readiness validator (must exit 0 to bind)
   * mai-healthcheck   - periodic local probe (systemd timer)
   * compliance dashboard - FastAPI operator console
   * config templates and trust-anchor directory layout
